					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p109554">Re: NES effectively 480p w/ black every other line &amp; 2x brig</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=109554#p109554"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Sat Mar 16, 2013 12:23 am&nbsp;</div></td>
